  ],
  "remarks": "Gennady Svetlov is the Director of JSC RPTP Granit (a.k.a. Ryazan Production and Technical Enterprise Granit). JSC RPTP Granit is a Russian military-industrial state enterprise that conducts maintenance and testing of weapons systems, including the S-400 Triumf and S-300 missile systems, deployed by the Russian Armed Forces. Moreover, JSC RPTP Granit is part of the Almaz-Antey concern, a Russian state-owned arms manufacturer that develops anti-aircraft defence and cruise missile systems for the Russian military.",
